{
  "id": "adv_event_2309_01_01",
  "title": "今のままで\nいいの？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは優し過ぎます！　そんなんじゃ……\n一生、トップアイドルになんてなれないのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚you’re too nice! At this rate…\nwe’ll never become top idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.5582991601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースがBIG4になってしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Sunny Peace became part of the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3582991601,
      "endTime": 11.3367115021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～……雑誌のインタビュー、おしまい！\nみんなお疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… Magazine interview‚done!\nGood work‚everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2700441997,
      "endTime": 20.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "インタビュアーさんが楽しい人で良かったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad the interviewer was a fun person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1713832221,
      "endTime": 24.9033333144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "一杯笑わせてくれたから……\nとっても、話しやすかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They made me laugh a lot…\nIt was easy to talk to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1150792124,
      "endTime": 29.8699999811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "この後のスケジュールは……お昼休憩を挟んで\n午後にラジオ収録、それからレッスンね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our schedule after this is… Lunch break‚\nthen radio recording in the afternoon‚followed by practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0817458791,
      "endTime": 39.9817462607,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2789.865684399995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "毎日スケジュールが詰まってて凄いわね\nBIG4の肩書きはそれだけ大きいってことかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have a packed schedule every day‚it’s amazing.\nI guess that’s what it means to be a BIG4 group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1934921585,
      "endTime": 48.7365303361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "（確かに、沢山お仕事をもらえるのは嬉しい。だけど……）\n（私が……私達が目指すのはトップアイドルだよね？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s great that we’re getting so much work‚but…）\n（I… We’re aiming to be top idols‚right?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.948276234,
      "endTime": 65.7066884044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、みんな。最近の私達って\n毎日仕事をこなすだけで一杯一杯になってない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚everyone. Lately‚haven’t we just been\nbusy with getting our work done?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9184343024,
      "endTime": 76.2390689537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……確かに、ちょっと目が回るくらい\n忙しい時もあるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It’s true that\nI feel a little dizzy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4508148515,
      "endTime": 84.6659645403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと休みはもらってるから、意外と大丈夫……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re getting proper breaks‚so it’s actually okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8777104383,
      "endTime": 88.8410438543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　大変だけど、楽しく頑張れてると思うよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! It’s tough‚but I think we’re doing our best and having fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2110412285,
      "endTime": 94.45807081909999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、みんな一つ一つのお仕事に目標を持って\n取り組んでるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚we’re all working towards goals\nfor each of our jobs‚right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.669816717,
      "endTime": 99.9053044642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんが心配する気持ちも分かるけど……\n充実した日々は送れてるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand why you’re worried‚Rei…\nbut I think we’re living fulfilling lives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1170503622,
      "endTime": 105.8170504576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……そうですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0287963556,
      "endTime": 111.5582523035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "（私も……いろんなお仕事が出来て、いろんな場所で）\n（ライブが出来て……楽しめてる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m… able to do various jobs‚and perform\nat different places… I’m enjoying it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7699982014,
      "endTime": 120.600496706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんの言う通り、充実はしてる）\n（今のままで十分……なのかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Like Haruko-san said‚it is fulfilling.）\n（But is this enough…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.812242604,
      "endTime": 131.3013581283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……っ！\nあ、もうこんな時間。そろそろ帰らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*Panting*……!\nAh‚it’s already this late. I should head back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4131223369,
      "endTime": 150.943462341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだろう、胸の奥にずっと何かが引っかかってる）\n（踊ったら少しはすっきりすると思ったけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What is this… There’s something that’s been bothering me.）\n（I thought dancing would clear my head a little…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1552082388,
      "endTime": 162.5158209173,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13065.610281000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "あれ……mihoさん？　お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… miho-san? Good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7609011659,
      "endTime": 170.46090126130002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様\nこんな時間まで練習していたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work.\nYou were practicing until this late?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6726471593,
      "endTime": 174.8003341845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "はい。……そうだ、この間は練習中にアドバイス\nしてくれてありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. …That’s right‚thank you for\ngiving me advice during practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.0120800823,
      "endTime": 185.02353971820003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "あれがアドバイスに聞こえるなんて能天気……いや\nストイックなのかしら。本当に厄介ね、貴方達は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think you took that as advice‚you’re so carefree… No‚\nstoic‚I suppose. You girls are truly troublesome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3426774513,
      "endTime": 194.1284820091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしよう、mihoさんに相談してみたいけど）\n（何を聞いたらいいのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What should I do… I want to talk to miho-san about this‚）\n（but what should I ask…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.251045116,
      "endTime": 202.06022798339998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、私は行くわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚I’ll be going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.2719738813,
      "endTime": 204.851338944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "あ……待って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Wait a moment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.063084842,
      "endTime": 208.2570531857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "あの……mihoさんから見て、残るBIG4の人達は\nどんな印象なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… What’s your impression\nof the other BIG4 members?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.4687990837,
      "endTime": 217.66879870219998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "残るBIG4……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other BIG4‚huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.8805446001,
      "endTime": 219.5921772572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
