      "text": "（怜ちゃん……最近ずっと様子がおかしいわよね）\n（今だって、無理に何かを隠したみたいだし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rei… She’s been acting strange lately.）\n（It’s like she’s trying to hide something.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 458.2080632473,
      "endTime": 466.9080628659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
