      "text": "あ、そういえば。遙子ちゃん\n今日はmihoさんとご飯に行くんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚that reminds me. Haruko‚\nyou’re going to dinner with miho-san today‚right?",
        "id": ""
