      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……あ、そうそう\n温泉旅館で迷惑を掛けちゃったから謝罪を兼ねて……ね",
